### =========================
### MUSCLELAB SEED DATA
### =========================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@password = password123


### =========================
### COACHES
### =========================

### Create coach Adam
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/users/coaches
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "adamcoach",
  "email": "adam.coach@gmail.com",
  "password": "{{password}}",
  "firstName": "Adam",
  "lastName": "Nowak",
  "age": 32,
  "experience": 7
}


