### =========================
### COACH SPECIALISATIONS
### =========================

### Adam specialisation
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/users/specialisation?specialisation=powerlifting
Authorization: Basic adamcoach {{password}}


### Bartek specialisation
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/users/specialisation?specialisation=bodybuilding
Authorization: Basic bartekcoach {{password}}


### Ola specialisation
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/users/specialisation?specialisation=mobility
Authorization: Basic olacoach {{password}}


### Tomek specialisation
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/users/specialisation?specialisation=strength
Authorization: Basic tomekcoach {{password}}


