### =========================
### TRAINING SLOTS
### =========================

### Adam slot 1
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/training-slots
Authorization: Basic adamcoach {{password}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "startTime": "2026-07-10T10:00:00",
  "endTime": "2026-07-10T11:00:00"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("adamSlot1", response.body.slotCode);
%}


