### =========================
### RESERVATIONS
### =========================

### Kacper reserves Adam slot 1
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/reservations
Authorization: Basic kacperclient {{password}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "trainingSlotCode": "{{adamSlot1}}"
}


### Michal reserves Bartek slot 1
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/reservations
Authorization: Basic michalclient {{password}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "trainingSlotCode": "{{bartekSlot1}}"
}


### Julia reserves Ola slot 1
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/reservations
Authorization: Basic juliaclient {{password}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "trainingSlotCode": "{{olaSlot1}}"
}


### Natalia reserves Tomek slot 1
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/reservations
Authorization: Basic nataliaclient {{password}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "trainingSlotCode": "{{tomekSlot1}}"
}


### =========================
### FINAL CHECKS
### =========================

### Public available slots
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/training-slots/client


### All coaches public
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/coaches


### Adam sees his slots
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/training-slots/coach
Authorization: Basic adamcoach {{password}}


### Kacper sees his reservations
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reservations/client
Authorization: Basic kacperclient {{password}}


### Adam sees his reservations
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/reservations/coach
Authorization: Basic adamcoach {{password}}